&lt;p&gt;We received the task to create a cost-effective alternative to flight simulators for Corendon Airlines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The pilots get to practice the de-icing procedure in VR supported by hand tracking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We collaborated closely with an experienced pilot to implement the features our target audience is looking for.&lt;/p&gt;
